title: Gareth Bale scores late to tie MLS Cup between LAFC and Phialdelphia Union | ESPN FC

media:group.media:title: Gareth Bale scores late to tie MLS Cup between LAFC and Phialdelphia Union | ESPN FC
media:group.media:description:
Gareth Bale scores with a header in stoppage time of the second extra time period to tie the MLS Cup at 3-3 and send it to a shootout.
